<P>The BEGGAR'S OPERA was repeated &s;eve|veral nights, and drew more money than any
<PB N="138" REF="137">
other play to the de&s;erted hou&s;e of Covent-Gar|den at that time. <Q><LIST>
<ITEM><LABEL>Macheath,</LABEL> Mr. BEARD.</ITEM>
